text: The Equity Party (; ), often known by the transliteration of its Arabic name, "El Insaf", is a political party in Mauritania. It was made on 3 July 2022 after Union for the Republic rebranded itself before the 2023 Mauritanian parliamentary election. It was led by Mohamed Melainine Ould Eyih. He left his position in the cabinet to focus on the leadership of the party before the 2023 Mauritanian parliamentary election. ==References== Category:Political parties in Africa Category:Politics of Mauritania Category:2022 establishments Category:2020s establishments in Africa
